8
00:00:39,670 --> 00:00:41,560
I've always seen you as one of my own.

9
00:00:42,390 --> 00:00:43,880
Now that your father is gone,

10
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:45,960
Ziyang and I

11
00:00:46,430 --> 00:00:48,000
will surely take good care of you.

12
00:00:53,670 --> 00:00:54,520
Don't worry, Yu.

13
00:00:55,150 --> 00:00:56,320
I'll take good care of you,

14
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:58,640
and my mom will look after your dad's company.

15
00:00:59,030 --> 00:01:01,070
Zhizhen needs no one to look after it.

16
00:01:09,560 --> 00:01:12,560
Congratulations to Zhizhen Group on this momentous occasion.

17
00:01:37,460 --> 00:01:40,580
[Beloved Father Su Qichao]

18
00:01:42,070 --> 00:01:43,150
Who are you?

19
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,920
Today is my father's funeral,

20
00:01:46,150 --> 00:01:46,700
yet you show up

21
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:47,790
with a bouquet of red flowers

22
00:01:47,790 --> 00:01:48,640
and say something like that?

23
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,870
That's completely inappropriate.

24
00:01:51,950 --> 00:01:55,000
I am Xiao Lang.

25
00:01:59,230 --> 00:02:01,070
He's the one who bought all the shares

26
00:02:01,070 --> 00:02:02,280
from Su Qichao.

27
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,280
How dare you come here?

28
00:02:04,710 --> 00:02:06,280
