65
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:12,000
Do you like it?

66
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,440
Yes.

67
00:04:12,630 --> 00:04:14,160
You're amazing, Mom.

68
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:16,350
