77
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,190
Why did he

78
00:04:33,190 --> 00:04:35,400
leave with Ms. Gao Rui?

79
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:37,040
Why did that little boy

80
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,920
say that Dad was his father?

81
00:04:39,350 --> 00:04:41,280
Does Dad not love me anymore?

82
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,790
My sweet child, I'm here with you.

83
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,280
Remember,

84
00:04:45,350 --> 00:04:46,640
no matter what happens,

85
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:50,080
I will always be by your side, protecting you

86
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,750
and loving you forever.

87
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:06,400
- Let go of me! - Mom!

88
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:08,160
- Let go of me! - Mom!

89
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:09,230
I am not sick at all!

90
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:11,480
- You have no right to take me away! - Mom!

91
00:05:13,670 --> 00:05:14,600
Let go of me!

92
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:18,430
Let go of my mom!

93
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:20,840
Mom.

94
00:05:22,110 --> 00:05:23,080
I'm back.

95
00:05:30,990 --> 00:05:32,840
Open the gate!

96
00:05:33,230 --> 00:05:34,430
This is my house!

97
00:05:34,670 --> 00:05:36,480
Open up! This is my house!

98
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,400
This

99
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:41,280
is my house now.

100
00:05:42,790 --> 00:05:43,520
Xiao Lang,

101
00:05:43,990 --> 00:05:45,600
