102
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,920
that you have to be so ruthless?

103
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:48,640
Ruthless?

104
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:51,960
Compared to what Su Qichao owed me,

105
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:53,080
